43
00:02:45,340 --> 00:02:50,295
may see there a regulatory burden he doesn't want to deal with.

44
00:02:50,295 --> 00:02:57,640
And so in many, many cases, the ships are registered in faraway places that

45
00:02:57,640 --> 00:03:03,910
are the maritime equivalent of offshore tax havens so that the ship

46
00:03:03,910 --> 00:03:12,690
owner can operate the ship more inexpensively, even if he is avoiding

47
00:03:12,690 --> 00:03:16,990
certain regulations that may be desirable regulations from the

48
00:03:16,990 --> 00:03:20,620
standpoint of the safety of the ship and the crew.

