85
00:06:15,690 --> 00:06:19,660
of all the global warming gases that are produced in the course of a year

86
00:06:19,660 --> 00:06:21,690
on planet Earth.

87
00:06:21,690 --> 00:06:27,410
The other sort of pollution are tiny particulates that come out of the

88
00:06:27,410 --> 00:06:29,000
smokestacks--

89
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:33,480
many, many thousands, millions of tons in the course of a year.

90
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:38,860
And if this particular material is carried ashore--

91
00:06:38,860 --> 00:06:44,060
and this will be especially harmful to people living along coastlines--

92
00:06:44,060 --> 00:06:47,530
then there are thousands and thousands, according to the

93
00:06:47,530 --> 00:06:53,820
