94
00:06:53,820 --> 00:07:00,400
by very fine particulate matter that they breathe and that originated

95
00:07:00,400 --> 00:07:03,560
coming out of the smokestack of a ship.

96
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:10,030
Why is this environmental pollution not more regulated than it is?

97
00:07:10,030 --> 00:07:15,030
