100
00:07:22,870 --> 00:07:29,510
would mean putting at least one observer on every ship and regulating

101
00:07:29,510 --> 00:07:38,240
exactly how the ballast water was handled in this port or in that port.

102
00:07:38,240 --> 00:07:42,600
The International Maritime Organization is not putting an

103
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:45,296
inspector on every ship out there.

104
00:07:45,296 --> 00:07:50,180
There is an assumption that the shipping companies are going to behave

105
00:07:50,180 --> 00:07:51,590
responsibly.

106
00:07:51,590 --> 00:07:55,350
