00:09:02,140 --> 00:09:02,810
dismantled.

123
00:09:02,810 --> 00:09:07,020
The ship owner says, it is no longer sufficient for me to

124
00:09:07,020 --> 00:09:08,030
operate this ship.

125
00:09:08,030 --> 00:09:15,130
And so what they do is that they rev up the engines, and they run the ship

126
00:09:15,130 --> 00:09:21,380
aground on a beach at high tide at the greatest speed they can manage.

127
00:09:21,380 --> 00:09:30,630
And at that point, thousands of poor workers are going to be taking the

128
00:09:30,630 --> 00:09:37,120
